raw_data.title: Director of Compliance
raw_data.description: The Compliance Director will act as the primary Operations contact for all Compliance and Quality Assurance-related projects.  This position is responsible for independently managing compliance related projects and providing consulting and contract services to clients for quality related issues and regulatory/ good manufacturing practices (GMP) compliance services.  This position is also responsible for designing, implementing, monitoring and maintaining ProPharma Group’s quality program, policies and strategies and ensuring company compliance to GMP regulations, internal procedures and policies in cooperation with peers.  This position will function as an Industry Thought Leader and Subject Matter Expert on all Compliance topics.
